
Warning!!! Critical Python incompatiblity encoutered.
This can occur if the users calls the GO-Elite python source code WITHIN A COMPILED version directory which results in critical conflicts between the compiled distributed binaries and the operating systems installed version of python. If this applies, either:
(A) double-click on the executable GO-Elite file (GO-Elite or GO-Elite.exe) or
(B) download the Source-Code version of GO-Elite and run this version (after installing any needed dependencies (see our Wiki or Documentation). Otherwise, contact us at: genmapp@gladstone.ucsf.edu

Installation Wiki: http://code.google.com/p/go-elite/wiki/Installation
